Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.34,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I have a big gun, I took it from my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.79,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sick with Justice, I just wanna feel you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.20,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm your angel, only a ring away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.55,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You make me violate you, no matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's all up to you, no one lives forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Been burn in the hell, by all those pigs out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.53,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's always been hell, from when I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:48.72,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They make me violate them, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:52.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs79}Get down on your knees! Get a good head on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.69,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}If it's for your guys, go to the end of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:59.00,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do what you think, give it with dedication...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:02.27,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll put out your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You made a mess! For Christ sakes, this rotten world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:09.10,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Shit out of luck! Go with my vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:12.54,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Light up the fire! Right on the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.90,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.48,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.39,0:01:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it? It looks smaller\Nthan I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has the proper air to it\Nfor an inheritance of the Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And such a fantastic array of color.\NIt's simply splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.90,0:01:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.41,0:01:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, although it may be\Na valuable inheritance...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the fact that so many of our resources\Nare being used for its retrieval...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.78,0:01:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Lord Alfred's passion and iron will\Nto make this painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the ideological basis for\Nan unstoppable...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...National Socialist movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.46,0:02:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon our success, he has promised\Nour party financial assistance...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as well as an introduction\Nto the Anti-communist Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although our party's numbers\Nare small in America...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this will be the opportunity we've\Nneeded to make a breakthrough.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.74,0:02:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped that their peculiar\Npolitical principle is different from ours...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but coming with that much\Nweaponry and equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is not something some poor\NCaucasians can pull off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their investment is obscenely out\Nof proportion to their objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.86,0:02:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about too much money for the job...\Nthe money we've been offered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.47,0:02:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty sharp, Rock.\NIt reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've also been hired with a lot\Nof money to get that painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It suggests great value. But it doesn't\Nmatch the artist's lack of fame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully that mystery will be\Nsolved tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock. Go fetch Revy some\Ndinner too, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.03,0:03:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her they don't deliver\Npizza out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.93,0:03:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she'll have to give in and eat\Nsomething from a can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's dinner. Dutch says to have\Nsomething to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.22,0:03:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... If this is about what happened\Nin the U-boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock. We're done talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.03,0:03:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason to go\Nover it again. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:03:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.02,0:04:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon is about to sink and the only\Nlight will be from the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as that happens,\Nwe'll raid their ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been keeping an eye on their ship\Nat the outer range of our radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. Revy and\NI will raid the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that they have what they wanted,\Nthey're probably sitting back, relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots can keep casually\Ntoasting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna come banging on our\Ntom-toms and raid you like Navajos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wagner won't even compare to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm gonna need you to take on\None more job, partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's your chance to go wild,\Ndischarging those lead bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.01,0:05:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You distract, I search. Make some noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I have no complaints if I can kill\Nwho I can kill and steal what I can steal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.03,0:05:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going, Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem glum, Revy.\NSomething happen with Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh no! Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first little piggy came to its end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oink, oink, oink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.41,0:06:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make my way to the upper deck\Nfrom the bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liven up the place with\Na big ruckus. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm gonna eat until I get my fill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.46,0:06:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that gunshot come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can go on a wild spree if they want,\Nbut tell them to stop shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.24,0:06:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! The enemy!\NThe enemy's made their way on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still going at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At times like these, what kinda face\Ndo we put on while we wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do we sit here looking bored,\Nsmoking and drinking beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you two were being shot at\Nearlier today, Dutch looked very calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.65,0:08:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I envied him. In any case, we're not\Nthe type who can sink bullets into people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we hold down the fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All squad leaders gather your men\Nin front of the dining room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assemble there and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard. Take aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, boy. They're only dressed\Nlike real soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is this where the boss is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You won't find the commander here!\NHe's on the upper level!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Revy? Revy? Where are you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it, that bitch!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Please wait. The crew here are\Nhired outsiders. S-So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So? So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether or not you're unaffiliated or\Nnon-resistant has nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.78,0:10:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're all insured,\Nthere's no problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oink, oink, oink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:11:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy. What the hell are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blitz! Punish the lawless hoodlums\Nwith a decisive shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.17,0:11:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I was just going\Nabout my job, Dicky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.69,0:11:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Creating a bloodbath is what\Nwe always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gunman is an occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who shoots based on their\Nmood is just a reckless shooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember hiring Charles Whitman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going wild and letting loose\Nis your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you screw up, I die too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be cool\Nas a cucumber, Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.61,0:11:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't handle that,\Nclimb a church and shoot all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.28,0:12:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're gonna lecture me too?\NDon't make me laugh, Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.75,0:12:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you expect, Two Hands?\NI'm your employer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were gonna kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought the same, partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No trust here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.35,0:12:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't even take a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's next, big boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The commander. We'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your Excellency. The enemy is likely{\i0}\N{\i1}those grave-robbers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our comrades are boldly{\i0}\N{\i1}countering and dealing with them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll be sure to get them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please do not worry, Your Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:13:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rachmann. Not once has{\i0}\N{\i1}a military unit been victorious...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...when entering a battle with{\i0}\N{\i1}nothing but desired observations.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please do not worry"\Nshows a lack of sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me what you base your\Nconfidence in your victory on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you should refrain\Nfrom such casual consolations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did I sound like I wanted an apology?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly, I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.10,0:13:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I place greater importance\Non your apology than the painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want the painting, and you are in\Nneed of connections into our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is clear and simple.\NYou better understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy. Have you cooled down a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.96,0:13:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get Whitman fever whenever\Nwe get a newcomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened when we took in Benny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.60,0:14:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our style's not to dig too deep\Ninto each other's past, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.91,0:14:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finish this job. Perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you will. Or we wouldn't\Nbe able to support our way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check this area.\NWe'll finish talking later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're still alive, little girl.\NI compliment your audaciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M y name is Blitz Stanford.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the acting captain of the glorious\NWhite Aryan Socialist Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fated confrontation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.90,0:14:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of those\Nwho died for the Union...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.67,0:14:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you shall atone with your blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.78,0:14:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This gun I proudly wield!\NI call it the Eiserne Reich Luger Special!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The base is the Luger artillery long\Nand the frame is hardened carbon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a thick grip and\Na double re-enforced chamber!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A 454 Casull is used, making it way too\Ndestructive to just be referred to as...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...specialized in man-stopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the only one on Earth who\Ncan wield this terrible gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid?\NThere's no way you're not afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the power of this gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not even listening. How long are you\Ngonna talk? Are you a televangelist?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you something worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All these things need to do\Nis fire and hit their target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that's a useful lesson.\NSay "hi" to the Fuhrer for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the sound of the finale.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that you've lost. I've heard\Nthat tune many times in my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.94,0:15:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just a distant memory to me now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.71,0:15:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nazi. I've come to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, given what we've been through,\NI don't think I'll apologize for being rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind me. I'll wait until you're\Ndone with the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He certainly is a brave man.{\i0}\N{\i1}I want to talk to him. Put him on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's for you.\N- Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You the boss? Your subordinates{\i0}\N{\i1}were a real waste.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. Forgive me for\Nthe shameful display.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've got two questions for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.55,0:16:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About what the painting really is?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then start with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another candidate for who\Npainted this piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...other than the commonly\Nbelieved artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I commend you on your research.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A former Bohemian artist...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.73,0:16:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Adolf Hitler himself.\NOr that's how rumor has it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fuhrer's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush to conclusions, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fuhrer as an artist could, at best,\Nonly do mediocre scenic pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It reminds me that the SS officer also\Nbelieved in that false information...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when he left for Batavia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.15,0:17:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what you want isn't the painting,\Nbut something else inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.93,0:17:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, this is just a guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you know the phone number\Nto our office, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The antique trade company from Madrid\Nthat asked for this salvage job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that was me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was also the one who wanted you{\i0}\N{\i1}and Rachmann to collide.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was a most amusing method...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.38,0:17:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...which also acted as their rite{\i0}\N{\i1}of passage and insurance for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, this is a fleeting\Nand dear memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.89,0:17:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day Heydrich decided\Non the "Final Solution"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we made a vow at the Wannsee\Nlakeside to become realistic guardians...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...rather than idealists\Nbelieving in victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gathered all of our capital\Nand created a file...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with all of our signatures\Nand account numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When signs of the end approached...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we placed our files into four paintings\Nand escaped Berlin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That painting there is the last piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have quite the insight,\NMr. Jungle Bunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch what you say, white man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might get upset and return it\Nto the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.06,0:18:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's fine. I simply wanted to get it{\i0}\N{\i1}back because it was discovered.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are a financial success...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what about the trust you might lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.31,0:18:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it, but you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're very wise.{\i0}\N{\i1}It's a shame you are black.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Now, please continue\Nwith your conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No. There's no need for that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.79,0:18:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has already fulfilled his role.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alfred! You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First you set me up in this fixed race,\Nand now you betray me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch your mouth, youngster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:18:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and the black man were...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.94,0:19:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...given equal terms.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should have known better than{\i0}\N{\i1}to try and enter our society...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...with that level of ability.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, black man. That was a splendid job.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.25,0:19:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you were an Aryan,{\i0}\N{\i1}I would send you an Iron Cross.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want one. All I want\Nis the money, you Gestapo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honesty is wonderful.\NHypocrisy rots this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that all people like you will be\Nwiped off the face of this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you kindly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I hope that you'll go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. You're not done cleaning up?\NIs that man the commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna make a bet, Dutch?\NYou know, the usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not much of a bet, Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it anyway. Here you go old man.\NUse it as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I say black.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. I say black too.\NIt's not much of a bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.82,0:20:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Told you. Not much of a bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I thought he might\Njust surprise us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.03,0:20:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all the same. Rotten by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn right. Let's finish this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure got the shivers today.\NToo much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. I won't cause any more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.62,0:21:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I know what you're hung up on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has more to do with\Nwhat's deep down inside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I n other words, you won't feel any better\Nno matter what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock's a guy that's on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's completely different from\Npeople on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't stand that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Dutch, it's just not possible. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't partner with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:18.52,Black Lagoon Next Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10\pos(980,916)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.72,0:23:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Shut up, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.49,0:23:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious! I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.79,0:23:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, then do it.
